videos.description: Sean O'Mara gets the ball in the post and spins to the baseline and gets the slam.
videos.headline: Xavier's O'Mara spins, finishes with flush

videos.description: Seton Hall guard Myles Powell drills the 3-pointer with the foul for the 4-point opportunity.
videos.headline: Seton Hall converts 4-point play

videos.description: Xavier's Trevon Bluiett hits his seventh 3-pointer in transition to pad the Musketeer lead.
videos.headline: Bluiett knocks down 7th 3-pointer of game

videos.description: Xavier's Trevon Bluiett converts his eighth 3-pointer of the night, from way downtown.
videos.headline: Bluiett nails 8th 3 way behind 3-point line

videos.description: Seton Hall's Ismael Sanogo blocks the 3-point attempt and saves it from going out of bounds, spurring the fast break 3-pointer by Myles Powell.
videos.headline: Seton Hall block leads to 3 on other end
